     fhir:value [
       a fhir:Markdown ;
       fhir:v "System that captures a laboratory test order for a patient and pushes it to the Lab Order Repository as a ZWLabOrderBundle transaction (FHIR `POST` of a transaction Bundle carrying ZWLabTask, ZWLabServiceRequest, ZWLabPatient and ZWSpecimen). In the Zimbabwe national architecture this role is played by the Impilo EHR (transaction ① — order push)."
